original_title: 松井玲奈・SKE48卒業コンサートin豊田スタジアム～2588DAYS～
overview: Matsui Rena SKE48 Graduation Concert in Toyota Stadium ~2588 DAYS~ (松井玲奈・ＳＫＥ４８卒業コンサートin豊田スタジアム～2588DAYS～) is an SKE48 Summer Concert that was held in Toyota Stadium on August 29 and August 30, 2015.
title: Matsui Rena SKE48 Graduation Concert in Toyota Stadium ~2588 DAYS~
